OL,3,CMaternity services make 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' following serious
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,FMaternity services at East Kent
OL,8,FHospitals have been rated as 'good' by
OL,9,Fthe Care Quality Commission (CQC).
OL,11,FInspectors say services at the William
OL,12,FHarvey Hospital in Ashford and the
OL,13,FQueen Elizabeth The Queen Mother
OL,14,FHospital (QEQM) in Margate have made
OL,15,Fsignificant improvements, since its
OL,16,Flast inspection in 2023.
