OL,3,CMaternity services make 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' following serious
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,FBoth units, which are run by East Kent
OL,8,FHospitals University NHS Foundation
OL,9,FTrust, were rated as 'good' for being
OL,10,Fcaring, effective, responsive and well-
OL,11,Fled, following an inspection in
OL,12,FDecember 2024.
OL,14,FThe team found that the women and
OL,15,Fbabies were protected and kept safe;
OL,16,Fthat the units were clean and well-
OL,17,Fmaintained; that there were enough
OL,18,Fstaff who were well-trained; and that
OL,19,Fthe units had a good learning culture,
OL,20,Fwhere people could raise concerns.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
