OL,3,CMaternity services make 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' following serious
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,FHowever, it found that the outdated
OL,8,Fhospital buildings meant some clinical
OL,9,Fareas and labour rooms in both units
OL,10,Fare too small and lack en suite
OL,11,Ffacilities, compromising the care
OL,12,Fstaff are able to give, and that there
OL,13,Fis currently only one obstetric
OL,14,Ftheatre at Queen Elizabeth The Queen
OL,15,FMother Hospital.
OL,17,FThe CQC therefore rated the units as
OL,18,F'requires improvement' for 'safe'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
