OL,3,CMaternity services make 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' following serious
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,FThe CQC's findings come three years
OL,8,Fafter Dr Bill Kirkup's damning report
OL,9,Finto standards of maternity services
OL,10,Fin East Kent.
OL,12,FThe investigation looked at hundreds
OL,13,Fof cases at the QEQM and William
OL,14,FHarvey Hospital from 2009 to 2020 and
OL,15,Ffound that if women and babies had
OL,16,Freceived nationally recognised
OL,17,Fstandards of care then 45 babies may
OL,18,Fhave survived, 12 babies may not have
OL,19,Fsuffered brain injury and 23 women who
OL,20,Fdied or were injured could have had a
OL,21,Fdifferent outcome.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
