OL,3,CMaternity services make 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' following serious
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,FEast Kent Hospitals University NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust Chief Executive,
OL,9,FTracey Fletcher, said: "The reports
OL,10,Fpublished by the CQC today reflect the
OL,11,Fsignificant hard work and dedication
OL,12,Fof staff across the maternity service.
OL,14,F"This is an important milestone in our
OL,15,Fcontinuing work to improve our
OL,16,Fservices and embed the lessons
OL,17,Foutlined in the 'Reading the Signals'
OL,18,Freport into our Trust, published by Dr
OL,19,FKirkup in 2022.
OL,26,@qD@XOUvD@AOU
