OL,7,F"I want to reiterate, particularly to
OL,8,Fthe families affected by the failings
OL,9,Fin care described in the 'Reading the
OL,10,FSignals' report, our commitment to
OL,11,Fcontinue to improve our services and
OL,12,Fwork to provide the highest standard
OL,13,Fof care for our communities."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
