OL,3,CMaternity services make 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' following serious
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,FSerena Coleman, CQC's deputy director
OL,8,Fof operations in Kent, said: "When we
OL,9,Finspected maternity services at both
OL,10,FWilliam Harvey Hospital and Queen
OL,11,FElizabeth The Queen Mother Hospital,
OL,12,Fwe found significant improvements and
OL,13,Fa better quality service for women,
OL,14,Fpeople using the service and their
OL,15,Fbabies.
OL,17,F"Our experience tells us that when a
OL,18,Fservice isn't well-led it's difficult
OL,19,Ffor them to provide good care in other
OL,20,Fareas.
OL,26,@pD@^OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
