OL,3,CMaternity services make 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' following serious
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,F"This turnaround in ratings across
OL,8,Fboth services demonstrates what can be
OL,9,Fachieved with strong and capable
OL,10,Fleaders who focus on an inclusive and
OL,11,Fpositive culture.
OL,13,F"We saw the positive impact of
OL,14,Fimproved staffing and culture at both
OL,15,Fhospitals. Women told us about feeling
OL,16,Fwell-supported throughout birth, with
OL,17,Fone QEQM mother describing how a
OL,18,Fmidwife stayed after her shift
OL,19,Ffinished to provide continuous support
OL,20,Fduring a difficult labour.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
