OL,3,CMaternity services make 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' following serious
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,F"Leaders had taken steps to improve
OL,8,Fthe physical environment across both
OL,9,Fhospitals where they were able to, and
OL,10,Fsafety risks posed by the estate and
OL,11,Fward environment were being managed
OL,12,Fand mitigated more effectively.
OL,14,F"However, concerns remain about the
OL,15,Fsize of the labour rooms which were
OL,16,Fnot always big enough to include
OL,17,Fessential equipment such as infant
OL,18,Fresuscitaires.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
