OL,4,Cimprovements' following serious
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,F"Resuscitaires were now located
OL,8,Fdirectly outside each labour room to
OL,9,Fensure quick access and avoid mothers
OL,10,Fand babies being separated for lengthy
OL,11,Fperiods of time in situations where
OL,12,Fbabies required resuscitation
OL,13,Ffollowing birth.
OL,15,F"Leaders had similar problems at QEQM
OL,16,Fhospital. The small room size and lack
OL,17,Fof air conditioning impacted on
OL,18,Fwomen's comfort and as at WHH, their
OL,19,Fability to move around freely during
OL,20,Flabour.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
